features: INSPIRED BY DISNEY’S BELOVED FILM: Inspired by Disney’s The Little Mermaid, join this Ariel doll's adventure as she goes from sea to land
FASHION TRANSFORMATION: Transform Ariel from a mermaid to human when changing her into her pink dress and shoes. Ariel is also able to stand on her molded mermaid tail

STORYTELLING ACCESSORIES: Along with a seashell bag and dinglehopper for styling Ariel’s hair, and a silver platter & lid, the set comes complete with friends Sebastian & Flounder to join her on any adventure
6” TALL, PERFECT FOR ON-THE-GO PLAY: Ariel stands at 6” tall with 5 points of articulation, at the neck, shoulders and hips, allowing her to be posed
GREAT GIFT IDEA: Makes a great birthday gift, holiday gift, or gift for Disney Princess fans

INCLUDES: 1 Ariel Doll, 1 Doll Outfit, 1 Doll Removable Mermaid Tail and Top, 1 Doll Tiara, 1 Pair of Doll Shoes, 1 Flounder, 1 Sebastian, 1 Doll Seashell Bag, 1 Dinglehopper, 1 Platter & Lid, 4 Chip Play Pieces
body.description: Play out favorite movie moments from Disney’s The Little Mermaid with the Sea and Land Ariel Petite Set. Transform Ariel from a mermaid to her pink land outfit, each with story inspired details! Recreate the magical moment when Ariel becomes part of the human world and embarks on her adventure. With a seashell bag, and tiara for accessorizing, style Ariel in her mermaid form. Lift the silver lid off the tray and find Sebastian hiding under! Ariel doll can join you on any adventure, along with friends Sebastian and Flounder. Perfectly petite in size and complete with 5 points of articulation, Ariel can be posed in so many ways, so the fun never ends!
